eICR Processing Warning Reason Codes

If the PHA system (or its intermediary) identifies an issue with the eICR, but is still able to process the file, this will contain those issues as a warning.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://acme.org/cdc-codes
    CodeDisplay
    invalid idINVALID ID (TEMPORARY CODE)
